s=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/9d56e5ac3808a8062e6b838086319ff8.avif?t=1772596219\" width=600 height=85 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2e0a1fc950e4dcac9d421e3741d50af2.poster.avif?t=1772596219\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2e0a1fc950e4dcac9d421e3741d50af2.webm?t=1772596219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736270/extras/2e0a1fc950e4dcac9d421e3741d50af2.mp4?t=1772596219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything you do adds up to the final score and evolution of the horde. How good are *<i>you</i>* at devouring your way to the end of humanity?</p>",
